[[Image:AntigonusGonatas.jpg|thumb|200px|Coin of [[Antigonus II Gonatas]]]]
The members of the Antigonid dynasty were:

{| class=&quot;wikitable&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;5&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; | style=&quot;margin: 1em auto 1em auto; width: 75%&quot;
